The Postman;;1997;;R;;Action,Adventure,Drama;;6.1;;Kevin Costner;;Kevin Costner,Will Patton,Larenz Tate,Olivia Williams,James Russo,Daniel von Bargen,Tom Petty,Scott Bairstow,Giovanni Ribisi,Roberta Maxwell,Joe Santos,Ron McLarty,Peggy Lipton,Brian Anthony Wilson,Todd Allen,Rex Linn,Shawn Hatosy,Ryan Hurst;;2013,Post-Apocalyptic America. An unnamed wanderer retrieves a Postman's uniform and undelivered bag of mail. He decides to pose as a postman and deliver the mail to a nearby town, bluffing that the United States government has been reinstated and tricking the town into feeding him. However, he reluctantly becomes a symbol of hope to the townspeople there who begin to remember the world that once was and giving them the courage to stand up to a tyrannical warlord and his army.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0119925/